accessibility.text: Kept team organized and on time with deadlines
Used previous game design experience to streamline ideation and iteration, since all other teammates were new to game design
Ideation + Iteration – brought my own ideas and tried to keep our iteration grounded in the original transformational goal
Research – connected research on mirror neurons, physical activity, and vulnerability to design decisions
User Testing – I usually like moderating playtests and observing things that the notetaker might not catch
Helped write manifesto on good Sleepy Game Design (abstracting experience)
